play-launch (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Phase 7: Logging Improvements
  * Refined I/O helper logging levels (DEBUG by default, visible with --verbose)
  * Added periodic node error monitoring (warns about high stderr activity)
  * Error monitoring configurable via config.yaml (threshold, interval, rate limit)
  * Fixed error monitoring to accumulate errors between warnings
  * Reduced default rate limit from 5 minutes to 1 minute for responsiveness

 -- Jerry Lin <jerry73204@gmail.com>  Mon, 04 Nov 2025 12:00:00 +0000

play-launch (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * ROS 2 launch inspection tool with resource monitoring
  * Optimized binaries (8.7MB total)
  * Multi-architecture support (x86_64, arm64)

 -- Jerry Lin <jerry73204@gmail.com>  Mon, 04 Nov 2025 04:00:00 +0000
